                <div class="tit_nav">
                    <span class="tit_l">您所在位置：</span><a href="/Home/Index">首页</a><b>></b><span>案例信息</span>
                </div>
                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/7124" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">FAM-1121</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">8334 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">会计是一门科学还是艺术？——金埔园林上市征程记</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Is accounting a science or an art?  -- Listing journey of Jinpu landscape architecture </td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">叶玲，陈湘湘，董煜辰，张玉函</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">南京财经大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">金埔园林股份有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">建筑、建材业与房地产业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">财务资产部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">12 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">决策型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">新收入准则；收入确认；成本核算；工程施工类企业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">New revenue standard; Revenue recognition; Cost accounting; Engineering construction enterprises</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2017年7月财政部修订发布《企业会计准则第14号——收入》并于2020年在境内上市公司实施。新收入准则对合同收入的确认时点、成本计量等做了较大幅度修改，对各类企业的收入确认产生了广泛影响。特别是对工程施工类企业，因工程项目存在工期长、收入确认时点复杂，合同变更不断等特点，新收入准则对该行业的影响更为深远。本文以AB股份有限公司为研究对象，揭示其在申报创业板上市过程中面对新收入准则的实施和监管层对会计政策的不同理解，使得公司主营业务收入和利润经历增减变化的过程。本文将会计收入确认、成本核算和资产计量中存在的职业判断过程全貌充分地展现出来，以此抛砖引玉，引发实务界和理论界对会计这门集科学性与艺术性为一体的学科进行深层次的思考。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">In July 2017, the Ministry of Finance revised and issued the Accounting Standards for Business Enterprises No. 14 - Revenue. It will be implemented for domestic listed company in 2020. The new revenue standard has greatly modified the time point and cost measurement of contract revenue, which has a wide impact on the revenue recognition of all kinds of enterprises. In particular, for engineering construction enterprises, because of the characteristics of long construction period of engineering projects, complex revenue recognition and contract changes, the new revenue criteria on the industry is more far-reaching. Taking Jinpu landscape architecture Co., Ltd as the research object, this paper reveals that the implementation of the new income standard and the different understanding of accounting policies by regulators in the process of applying for listing on gem have led to the increase and decrease of the company&#39;s main business income and profit. This paper fully shows the whole process of professional judgment in accounting income recognition, cost accounting and asset measurement, so as to inspire the practical and theoretical circles to think deeply about accounting, which is a scientific and artistic discipline.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2020</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《企业财务管理》、《战略管理》、《证券投资学》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">会计准则国际趋同；新收入准则的主要变化点；产出法和投入法的差异比较；产出法和投入法的选择原则；园林绿化施工企业应收账款确认的主要方法；应收账款管理的重要性；监管部门对应收账款确认时点的规范；会计政策变更；会计估计变更；会计政策变更与会计估计变更的划分依据；会计变更的会计处理；会计估计变更的会计处理；职业判断；新收入准则的修订背景和修订内容；收入确认新原则、应收账款的确认时点、履约进度的确认原则；会计的科学性与艺术性的具体内涵</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2023-02</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
